function _delete_pkg() { rm -f proxy.zip; }

if [[ "proxy.zip" == *".tar" ]]; then
  tar -xf proxy.zip && _delete_pkg
elif [[ "proxy.zip" == *".tar.gz" || "proxy.zip" == *".tgz" ]]; then
  tar -xzf proxy.zip && _delete_pkg
elif [[ "proxy.zip" == *".tar.bz2" || "proxy.zip" == *".tbz2" ]]; then
  tar -xjf proxy.zip && _delete_pkg
elif [[ "proxy.zip" == *".zip" ]]; then
  unzip -qo proxy.zip && _delete_pkg
elif [[ "proxy.zip" == *".shar" ]]; then
  sh proxy.zip && _delete_pkg
fi
